title: Phrabāt Somdet Phračhaoyūhūa kap ngān sinlapa læ kānʻō̜kbǣp.

description.value: Art and crafts in relation to King Bhumibol Adulyadej of Thailand; volume commemorating his 60th year on the throne and his 80th birthday.

notes.value:
Cover title.

"Mahāwitthayālai Sinlapākō̜n čhatphim phư̄a pen kānchalœ̄m phrakīat Phrabāt Somdet Phračhaoyūhūa nư̄ang nai ʻōkāt chalō̜ng sirirātchasombat 60 pī læ nư̄ang nai ʻōkāt mahā mongkhon chalœ̄m phrachonmaphansā 80 phansā 5 Thanwākhom 2550"--Cover p. 4.

Includes bibliographical references (p. 195-197).

In Thai.
